The paper deals with decentralized sequential detection with conditionally independent observations, which involves wireless communication and signal processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also deals with control and decision-making, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper involves optimization and statistical analysis, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MA (Machine Learning). The paper involves networked systems, which suggests that it could belong to cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Finally, the paper involves simulations and signal processing, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
